<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>For The Releast Girlfriend Out There</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b);
            color: white;
            font-family: "Old English Text MT", "Blackletter", Georgia, serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .letter {
            max-width: 800px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .heart {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .letter {
                padding: 25px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="letter">

        <div class="heart">❤️</div>

        <h1>To My Favorite Person</h1>

        <p>
            Aye these words just gone come out how I think em
            but I wanted u to know whats been on my mind.
        </p>

        <p>
            Out of everybody I could be spending my time with, talking to,
            or giving my energy to. It would be u everytime. Not cuz we 
            ain had our obstacles but cuz no matta what u genuinely someone
            I rock wit.
        </p>

        <p>
            U done seen me at some of my best and worst moments.
            U done seen me overthink, stress, get in my own
            head, and still be here. I dont take that lightly.
        </p>

        <p>
            I know I dont always say things the right way, and sometimes
            I make stuff harder than it gotta be, but one thing I never
            want u questioning is how much u mean to me.
        </p>

        <p>
            Whether we laughing, sitting in silence, on the phone
            late at night, or counting down til we see each other again,
            moments like dat matter to me.
        </p>

        <p>
            U became a part of my life in a way I wasnt expecting
            and if I'm being real. I dont want to imagine a future where
            ur not in it.
        </p>

        <p>
            At the end of er day all I want is for u to know that
            I'm still here and thankful that out of everybody
             in the world, somehow our paths crossed.
        </p>

        <div class="signature">
            Love,<br>
            A Lucky Dude Named Harold 
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
